---
title: Do I need bunting today?
description: Find out if today is a bank holiday that needs bunting if you're in England, Wales, Scotland or Northern Ireland
layout: layouts/base
eleventyComputed:
  bunting: "{{ 'true' if bank_holidays.bunting }}"
---

<div class="page-content">
  <span class="answer">
    {% if bank_holidays.bunting %}
      Yes!
    {% else %}
      No.
    {% endif %}
  </span>
  {% if bank_holidays.bankHoliday %}
    {% if bank_holidays.bunting %}
      <span class="subtext">If you're in {{ bank_holidays.buntingLocations | sentencejoin("or") }}</span>
    {% else %}
      <span class="subtext">Today is a bank holiday in
        {{ bank_holidays.bankHolidayLocations | sentencejoin("and") }}, but you don't need bunting
      </span>
    {% endif %}
  {% else %}
    <span class="subtext">Today isn't a bank holiday in the UK</span>
  {% endif %}
</div>
